                                                        Period Days
                                                        <p>It's that time again. As the lining of your uterus sheds, your period starts. This is also the official start of your cycle. Want to know more? Here are answers to <a data-action-detail="periodcalculator_perioddays_10periodquestions" class="event_view_more_details" href="/en-us/tips-and-advice/your-first-period/10-common-period-questions">10 common period questions</a>. And make sure you’re stocked up on ALWAYS pads!</p><img alt="" height="240" width="255" src="-/media/FBDAA5CBC77941DAAC2C90CBBB29244A.ashx">
