                                                        Post-Period
                                                        <p>Your bleeding has stopped - or at least lightened up a lot by now. Here are more details about the <a data-action-detail="periodcalculator_postperiod_4menstrualcyclephases" class="event_view_more_details" href="/en-us/tips-and-advice/your-first-period/your-menstrual-cycle-phases">4 menstrual cycle phases</a> if you’d like more details. Because every month is a little different, carry ALWAYS pantiliners with you just in case.</p><img alt="" width="255" height="240" src="-/media/8F91ABE5CF69425F87C16438AEC55969.ashx">
